precis:
Amendments to the COLLISION REGULATIONS which revoke obsolete provisions
dealing with signals, incorporate international requirements respecting the
positioning and spacing of navigation and signal lights, require a survival
craft to be fitted with a locating signal, and clarify the identification
characteristics of Ocean Data Acquisition System buoys.
